CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 8, 1958, pg. A15 reads: "Graduate Hosts Party - Miss Fay Ann Devereaux was hostess at this party following her graduation from Westinghouse High School. Among the many guests were Sam Gibson, Phyllis Byrd, Patricia Prattis, Hiram Baker, Barbara Brooks, Richard Hancock, Ann Stroud, Gloria Williams, Bruce Kimbro, Darlene Daniels, Loretta Lyman and Clavin Lee. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group of young adults, including Sam Gibson, Phyllis Byrd, Patricia Prattis, Hiram Baker, Barbara Brooks, Richard Hancock, Ann Stroud, Gloria Williams, Bruce Kimbro, Darlene Daniels, Loretta Lyman, and Clavin Lee, dancing at graduation party for Fay Ann Devereaux, another version
